      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented test suite covering all physics modules used in hemolysis simulation; change log maintained.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 is deployed under an ISO 9001-compliant QMS. All relevant solver modules are covered by vendor verification test suite. Version control and build records are archived."
    },
    {
