      "acceptanceCriteria": "Minimum five independent experimental replicates per operating point with inter-replicate coefficient of variation below 10% for hemolysis index.",
      "rationale": "Eight independent test runs performed at each of the five operating points using freshly prepared bovine blood lots. Inter-replicate CV ranged 3.1–7.8%, within the 10% acceptance threshold."
    },
